summary: An Ordinance providing for the purchase of certain portions of the Southeast one-quarter (1/4) of the Southeast one-quarter (1/4) of Section Nine (9), Township Twenty-four (24) North, Range Four (4) East, W. M., for the extension of Winthrop Street, from Rainier Avenue to Thirtieth Avenue South, for park and parkway purposes, for a sum not to exceed Five Thousand Dollars ($5,000.00), said sum to be paid from the Park Fund of the City of Seattle.
